nodes.text: LAAC was a destination on the subtram in the Coruscant Underworld. It was listed on travel maps inside the subtram trains, along with Sunset, Valley Village, North Hollywood, Beverly Blvd, Burbank, Lucasville, Filoniville, Laurel Canyon, Couch House, Skinwalker, RGC, Letterman, Skywalker Ranch, Big Rock Ranch and Skinwalker Ranch.

LAAC was inserted onto a subtram map as an in-joke by the Star Wars: The Clone Wars production team along with the other destinations on the map, referencing the Los Angeles Area Council in Los Angeles, California.
